                        <img src="~/images/waste 1.jpg" alt="AI in Waste Management" class="img-fluid rounded shadow" />
                        <div class = "hover-description">The Sensor tells you what is in your container, where it’s located, its fill level, pickup alerts, and the type of contamination impacting in your bins.
                        <a href="https://www.rts.com/pello-smart-bin-sensors/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Pello</a></div>
                    </div>
