                        <img src="~/images/waste 2.jpg" alt="AI in Waste Management" class="img-fluid rounded shadow" />
                        <div class = "hover-description">Nando is an AI solution capable of monitoring, analysing and measuring waste production, 
                        offering valueable insights on recycling and waste reduction. 
                        <a href="https://aiforgood.itu.int/revolutionizing-waste-management-the-role-of-ai-in-building-sustainable-practices/#:~:text=NANDO%20is%20the%20Artificial%20Intelligence,optimize%20their%20waste%20management%20procedures." target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Nando</a></div>
                    </div>
